msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:163
msgid ""
"Each user in the chat room will have a colored symbol beside their name where blue\n"
"            means that they are active, yellow means that they are idle, and red means that they are away."
msgstr ""

#: app/scripts/lx-directives/lx-landing-page-directives.js:144
msgid "Enter!"
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:131
#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:99
msgid "How to use ChatSurfing"
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:142
msgid ""
"If you have entered into a \"Popular chat\" that already has people chatting, then just say hello to\n"
"                people in the room and join in the conversation.\n"
"                Please note that to protect our members privacy, messages sent before you joined the\n"
"                room will not be displayed to you."
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:139
msgid ""
"If you want to have a private conversation with someone, then enter a unique chat room name that is\n"
"                unlikely to be accidentally chosen by other people. Then invite your friends to join\n"
"                you by sharing your chosen room name (send them an email, text message, etc.)."
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:146
msgid ""
"If you want to request a video exchange with someone, then click on the camera symbol beside\n"
"                their name and wait for them to accept or deny your offer."
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:158
msgid ""
"If you wish to see who has invited you to exchange video, click on the button at the top\n"
"                left beside the ChatSurfing logo, and select \"Notifications\".\n"
"                The notifications menu can also be seen by swiping left on a touch-sensitive device."
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:18
msgid "Join a chat room"
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:137
msgid ""
"Join a chat room from the main page by either typing in the name of a custom room, or by\n"
"                clicking on one of the \"Popular Chats\" that are listed."
msgstr ""

#: app/scripts/lx-directives/lx-landing-page-directives.js:119
msgid "Join!"
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:31
msgid "Name of chat room to create and/or join"
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:166
msgid "Supported browsers and devices"
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:162
msgid "To exit a chat room, click on the \"X\" symbol beside the chat room name, just below the ChatSurfing logo."
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:169
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, due to technical limitations video functionality does not work on iPhones or iPads. We\n"
"                hope to build an app in the future to allow support for these devices."
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:168
msgid "Video functionality is supported in Google Chrome, Firefox and Opera web browsers. We recommend using Chrome."
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:151
msgid ""
"You can open as many chats as you like. Just click on the button in the top left corner on the left side\n"
"                of the ChatSurfing logo to see the option for \"New chat\". You can also show the menu by swiping from\n"
"                left to right on a touch-sensitive device."
msgstr ""

#: app/lx-templates/lx-landing-page-main.html:155
msgid ""
"You can open video sessions with as many people as you like, however if your browser starts to slow down\n"
"                this is a sign that you have probably opened too many video sessions."
msgstr ""
